{"tid":1252677,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"【付費唔使愁】無信用卡都可以網購！3個唔使申請網上付費辦法！","createTime":"2019-06-23T06:41:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-23T06:41:49.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"fe043b00d5b9918e52d327150e11e67b74a21e33","tid":1252677,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T06:41:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190620/59734736\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190620%2F59734736&d=UYGl2U%2FUD6QdVJGaYMmpaGyAt0yGCUsyxQooKadsmXE%3D&h=cdc09ff9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190620%2F59734736&h=19b9e1d4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190620/59734736</a><br />\n<br />\n【付費唔使愁】無信用卡都可以網購！3個唔使申請網上付費辦法！<br />\n <br />\n網購必讀！想享受網上購物、訂閱付費、手遊課金的方便和樂趣，但又沒有信用卡，或擔心網上輸入信用卡資料？不用愁，蘋果即刻教你3個快捷方便辦法。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n方法一：八達通O! ePay<br />\n<br />\n在八達通O! ePay APP連結你的八達通號碼，開通當中可增值的虛擬白金預付卡O! ePay Mastercard。然後到APP內的「轉入」畫面進行增值，方法有四種：<br />\n1. 直接在NFC相容的手機（例如Samsung手機）用自己或朋友的實體八達通拍卡增值；<br />\n2. 透過「轉數快」從銀行戶口過數增值；<br />\n3. 到指定商戶出示八達通O! ePay APP內的二維碼（QR code）以現金增值，而最少增值額為港幣$50；<br />\n4. 從渣打銀行賬戶轉賬至個人O! ePay戶口。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n方法二：TAP &amp; GO「拍住賞」<br />\n<br />\n親身前往任何一間HKT、1O1O、csl、SUN Mobile門市免費領取TAP &amp; GO「拍住賞」實體卡，又或到7-Eleven、OK便利店購買TAP &amp; GO「拍住賞」Mastercard實體卡，跟隨指示將卡連接到TAP &amp; GO「拍住賞」APP。而只要你年滿11歲或以上，即可啟動TAP &amp; GO「拍住賞」賬戶，在APP內的左上角目錄選擇「增值」，再到各門市或便利店用現金增值，便可以當作信用卡使用。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n方法三：MASTERCARD禮品卡<br />\n<br />\n市面上亦有港幣$500的MASTERCARD禮品卡，有效期為一年，毋須登記，即買即用。<br />\n衝破要有信用卡才可網上付費這道防線，為網購、訂閱、手遊課金作準備，你準備好今日就為你的網上生活增值了嗎？<br />\n-----------------------------<br />\n<br />\n你撐蘋果 我捐$1<br />\n支援反送中抗爭者  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190620/large/1561011500_b249.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190620%2Flarge%2F1561011500_b249.jpg&h=3b3c5525&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n沒有信用卡？不緊要，現在教你3個付費方法！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190619/large/1560943916_3d4e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190619%2Flarge%2F1560943916_3d4e.jpg&h=07414528&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n八達通O! ePay內有Mastercard的功能。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190619/large/1560943916_1505.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190619%2Flarge%2F1560943916_1505.jpg&h=0131b355&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n先連結自己的八達通號碼，按「轉入」，選擇增值方法。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190620/large/1561010233_d0f6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190620%2Flarge%2F1561010233_d0f6.jpg&h=a63ae399&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n你亦可以在指定商戶以現金增值，例如到便利店掃描二維碼（最少增值港幣50元）。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190619/large/1560943914_4282.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190619%2Flarge%2F1560943914_4282.jpg&h=43fb1a24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n另一個方法就是用Tap &amp; Go。你可以親身前往任何一間HKT、1O1O或 csl. 門市免費領取「拍住賞」實體卡。或者到特約零售商（7-Eleven、OK便利店或SUN Mobile門市）購買「拍住賞」Mastercard實體卡。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190619/large/1560943914_3eeb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190619%2Flarge%2F1560943914_3eeb.jpg&h=e733c771&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n免費取得「拍住賞」實體卡後，跟着指示把卡連結到Tap &amp; Go的應用程式。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190620/large/1561010382_41dd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190620%2Flarge%2F1561010382_41dd.jpg&h=23e6b03e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n按左上角目錄，選擇「增值」，再到各門市或便利店用現金增值，便可以當作信用卡使用。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190619/large/1560943911_6860.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190619%2Flarge%2F1560943911_6860.jpg&h=9b7d5cd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n只要你年滿11歲或以上，即可啟動「拍住賞」賬戶。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190619/large/1560943918_2288.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190619%2Flarge%2F1560943918_2288.jpg&h=a0347554&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n還有一個很方便的方法，就是給港幣500元，買萬事達卡禮品卡。即買即用，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>無須登記</strong></span></span>，不過留意有效期為一年。"}]}